Description:
All the hard work has been done
Take note investors and first home buyers! This charming three bedroom home is ideally positioned in a quiet avenue and is within easy walking distance to the CBD. The home has been restumped and tastefully renovated throughout and includes a cosy lounge area with a feature fireplace. The newly renovated kitchen comprises of dual fuel cooker, dishwasher and has loads of bench space and storage and overlooks the meals/family area. The master bedroom features beautiful polished timber floors and built in robes. The family bathroom has recently undergone a renovation which features bath, separate shower and vanity. There is also a large separate laundry big enough to accommodate a second fridge/freezer. Climate throughout is controlled by gas ducted heating and evaporative air conditioning with the added bonus of a solid fuel heater to the kitchen/meals area. Externally there is an outdoor entertaining area, sensational sized carport and a 6x6m (approx.) shed. Dont hesitate, this property wont be on the market for long!

Description:
Why would you build when you can have all this now
This stunning 22sq Metricon home was only completed in March 2017. This home is sure to impress with its family friendly layout and its focus on entertaining. The centrally located luxurious kitchen brings the family together with its oversized island bench, dual fuel cooker, walk in pantry and loads of storage. It overlooks a spacious family and meals room which opens out to the decked alfresco living. The home also offers a second living area which is ideal for a home theatre room. The master bedroom suite offers ensuite and walk in robe with the remaining three bedrooms all generous in size and comprising of built in robes. The family bathroom is modern and services the childrens wing of the home. The laundry has inset trough and even more storage with a walk in linen. Externally the home has been beautifully landscaped and offers an additional decked entertaining area to truly enjoy those summer nights. There is also a double garage with direct access into the home. Everything has been thought of in this quality home with additional features such as solar electricity panels, in-ground sprinklers and loads more features too numerous to mention.
